# NOTE: service-account.json MUST NOT be excluded here.
# Per LLM_HANDOVER.md: ".gcloudignore: Must not block service-account.json,
# or the bot will deploy but fail to download attachments or send async Chat
# messages." It is .gitignored so it never enters version control, but it
# DOES need to be uploaded with the source on every deploy.
